name: RTH London Zip Hoodie - Burgundy / Charcoal
description:
RTH London Zip Hoodie

Custom Fit

S - 36' / M - 40' / L - 42' / XL - 44' 

Finest Cotton Blend material

A must have for any winter wardrobe. Looks great matched with an RTH Beanie!

- Full zip hoodie with metal zip
- Slim fit
- Contrast sleeves and hood
- Twin needle stitching detailing
- Double fabric hood
- Contrast flat white drawcords
- Kangaroo pouch pocket
- Right hand side pocket has small hidden opening for earphone cord feed
- Hidden ear phone loops
- Ribbed cuff and hem
- Worldwide Responsible Accredited Production (WRAP) certified production

Sent by Royal Mail 1st Class Delivery. Dispatch within 3 working days, al please allow up to 7 working days from time of order.
International shipping please allow up to 28 days.
